data.description: Tucked away on a mature wooded lot in Broadacres, this class brick split-foyer has all the hallmarks of the style: main level living space plus lower level family room w/fireplace. Kitchen w/island leads to formal dining as well as an all-seasons sunroom. Three main level bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms plus fourth bedroom and third full bath down. 2 car attached side entry garage, fenced backyard. New HVAC and water heater. Room for all in a supremely convenient Powell location!
